The tau2 airline evaluation data and evaluation methodology in this directory are
derived from τ-bench / τ²-bench / τ³-bench by Sierra Research:

  https://github.com/sierra-research/tau-bench
  https://github.com/sierra-research/tau2-bench (dev/tau3 branch)

Task data (tasks.json) updated to τ³-bench v1.0.0 which includes 75+ task
quality fixes across all domains (27 airline task corrections).

